yaml-filter
------------------------------------------
YAML document filtering for libyaml

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libyaml-path-devel-0.2.0-1bl2
  libyaml-path0-0.2.0-1bl2
  libyaml0_2-0.2.5-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libyaml-devel-0.2.5-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/OpenSCAP/yaml-filter

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/OpenSCAP/yaml-filter/archive/refs/tags/v0.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack yaml-filter-0.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./yaml-filter-0.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/yaml-filter-0.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/yaml-filter-0.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libyaml-path0-0.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libyaml-path-devel-0.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(yaml-filter)
  /usr/bin/yamlp.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/yaml-filter.README
  /usr/share/doc/yaml-filter/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/yaml-filter/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/yaml-filter/developer.md
  /usr/share/doc/yaml-filter/yaml_path_v1.md

(libyaml-path0)
  /usr/bin/cygyaml-path-0.dll

(libyaml-path-devel)
  /usr/include/yaml-path.h
  /usr/lib/libyaml-path.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/yaml-filter.pc

------------------

